rows.label: tlk70000051_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, you lot. Have you ever
found a Secret Area?

rows.label: tlk70000051_01_msg0002
rows.name:
They're not something you can just
stumble across, but if you put in the
work they're usually something special.

rows.label: tlk70000051_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Sometimes they'll be incredible views,
other times they might be ancient ruins
or historical monuments. Depends.

rows.label: tlk70000051_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Secret Areas are pretty great.
I've never seen one myself, like.
Always wanted to. Imagine it!

rows.label: tlk70000051_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Bet you could dine out on a story like
that for a lifetime. Just think how many
drinks people'd buy you to hear it.
